<pre><code>factorial(int n)
{
    for(int i=1, f = 1; i&lt;=n; i++)
        f *= i;
    return f;
}
</code></pre>
 <p><strong>C/C++</strong>: Procedural</p>

<pre><code>unsigned long factorial(int n)
{
    unsigned long factorial = 1;
