 <h1>F#: Functional</h1>

<h3>Straight forward:</h3>

<pre><code>let rec fact x = 
    if   x &lt; 0 then failwith "Invalid value."
    elif x = 0 then 1
    else x * fact (x - 1)
</code></pre>

<h3>Getting fancy:</h3>

