 <h1>Python: Functional, One-liner</h1>

<pre><code>factorial = lambda n: reduce(lambda x,y: x*y, range(1, n+1), 1)
</code></pre>

<p>NOTE:</p>

<ul>
<li>It supports big integers. Example:</li>
</ul>

